  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Achieving Continuous Education in Secondary Schools (AcCESS) in Borno State, Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ActionAid UK&apos;s has a partnership with People&apos;s Postocde Lottery and benefits directly from lottery draws assigned within a calendar year. This PPL-funded project is for Nigeria Achieving Continuous Education in Secondary Schools (AcCESS) in Borno State. This project aims to train 20 teahcers to provide after-school support to 200 children to improve their educational outcomes, particularly within a crisis affected context. This is done through teacher trainining, engagement with school-based committees, as well as support to students.</narrative>
  </description>
